last_episode_to_air.name: Evie (Part Two)
last_episode_to_air.overview: At their college reunion, Evie and Dylan encounter a ex-boyfriend of Evie's. Luke tries to avoid dealing with his feelings. Angus concocts a plan to look more accomplished to his former college friends.

name: Lovesick
overview: After finding out he has an STI, Dylan must get back in touch with every girl he has ever had sex with to let them know the bad news.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: A conflicted Dylan tries to sort out his tangled romantic life in the present as he continues to track down his former flings.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Evie must come to terms with her feelings for Dylan, just as his relationship with Abigail gets more serious. Meanwhile Luke struggles in his new quest for love and Angus faces the reality of marrying someone he barely knows.

episodes.name: Abigail
episodes.overview: Dylan must contact all the girls he has slept with to inform them he has chlamydia. He casts his mind back to Abigail and a flashback reveals a defining moment he'd tried to forget...

episodes.name: Anna
episodes.overview: In  a flashback to 18 months ago, Luke is enjoying the best sex of his life  with psychology student Cleo, but he's keen to avoid deep conversation  in case she realises that he's actually quite shallow.

episodes.name: Cressida
episodes.overview: In  a flashback to 10 months earlier, Luke drags Dylan and Evie to a posh  party in the country. Luke is desperate to sleep with his childhood  crush Ilona, who's on his 'things to do before I die' list.

episodes.name: Jane
episodes.overview: In  a flashback to three years earlier, it's Evie's birthday and she plans  to tell Dylan about her feelings for him over a quiet dinner, but the  evening gets hijacked by their friends.

episodes.name: Bethany
episodes.overview: In  a flashback to four years earlier, Dylan panics that he's in a serious  relationship with Bethany, while Luke has trouble with his new boss  Diana.

episodes.name: Phoebe
episodes.overview: Dylan  sets about tracking down Phoebe who hasn't returned any of his  messages. This prompts a flashback to six years ago when the gang are at  a pub quiz.

episodes.name: Frankie
episodes.overview: After confessing his feelings to Evie, Dylan flashes back to an ill-fated weekend in the country with the gang and his hippie girlfriend, Frankie.

episodes.name: Agata
episodes.overview: Dylan starts seeing Abigail, the hotel clerk from Angus's wedding. Six years earlier, he meets Evie for the first time at a house party.

episodes.name: Amy
episodes.overview: Angus's friends encourage him to start dating after his divorce. Dylan hears back from Amy and remembers a fling that put him in an awkward position.

episodes.name: Liv
episodes.overview: Dylan looks at a flat with Abigail, and Luke goes to therapy. Three and a half years ago, Angus and Helen are engaged -- and at each other's throats.

episodes.name: Isabel
episodes.overview: At a whiskey tasting, Evie, Dylan and Luke think back on a drunken awards ceremony, where things didn't quite go as planned for any of them.

episodes.name: Emma
episodes.overview: Dylan meets up with his old girlfriend Emma. In a flashback, Evie and Dylan feel pressured on Valentine's Day, while Luke woos an ex.

episodes.name: Jonesy
episodes.overview: Dylan reconnects with Jonesy, a friend who doesn't recall sleeping with him. Three months earlier, the guys try to cheer him up with a wild night out.

episodes.name: Abigail (Part 2)
episodes.overview: The day after Angus's divorce party, Abigail won't answer Dylan's calls. He, Luke and Evie try to piece together what happened the night before.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: A conflicted Dylan tries to sort out his tangled romantic life in the present as he continues to track down his former flings.

episodes.name: Andi and Olivia
episodes.overview: Dylan and the group attends Abigail's Literary Festival. Meanwhile Evie feels jealous that herself and Dylan had years to figure things out, while him and Abigail seem to be doing just fine. Evie moves in with Luke.

episodes.name: Bonnie
episodes.overview: Dylan forgets to cancel Evie's hen party. The gang, along with Evie's cousin, spend the afternoon soap-making, and at karaoke.

episodes.name: Abigail (Part 3)
episodes.overview: The love triangle between Dylan, Evie, & Abigail comes to a climax, while Luke is looking for love in a nightclub.

episodes.name: Evie
episodes.overview: Dylan, Luke & Angus all experience complications in their love lives.

episodes.name: Martha
episodes.overview: A surprise party for Dylan's parents brings out a buried secret. Luke gets lost while Angus finds a kindred spirit.

episodes.name: Queen of Cups
episodes.overview: Luke is forced to confront his feelings about Jonesy at a fair. Angus examines his past relationships.

episodes.name: Tasha
episodes.overview: Dylan stumbles across the last name on his list - his ex, Tasha, who is opinionated to say the least.

episodes.name: Evie (Part Two)
episodes.overview: At their college reunion, Evie and Dylan encounter a ex-boyfriend of Evie's. Luke tries to avoid dealing with his feelings. Angus concocts a plan to look more accomplished to his former college friends.
